{"tid":628882,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"網店/樓上鋪/零售/創業 廣告宣傳交流","createTime":"2018-04-14T09:05:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T09:05:59.000Z","uid":110749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"797902ba331f185154780842f45f56afd42fbb31","tid":628882,"uid":110749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T09:05:59.000Z","msg":"有無人做緊同類野？？我一月開始做網店<br />\n整左個網頁 可以自已自助比錢 落單<br />\n開左個FACEBOOK PAGE 同 IG<br />\n<br />\n一開始唔係好我識FACEBOOK落廣告，倒左好多錢落去都無乜成效<br />\n大部份錢去不停試，儲左千零個LIKE<br />\n但發覺FACEBOOK PAGE，一唔比錢做廣告<br />\n出個新POST，得一百 幾十人接觸到，勁少互動，好難做<br />\n<br />\n之後轉左IG試下，而家儲左三千幾FOLLOW<br />\n落廣告無得好似FACEBOOK咁多SETTING<br />\n出POST多左人LIKE～多左人問價，但大多數都係齋LIKE唔買<br />\n不過IG感覺上無FACEBOOK PAGE咁仆街<br />\n唔比錢就睇唔到你個POST<br />\n<br />\n錢就賺得唔多，大半都貢獻哂落去做廣告<br />\n每個月 平均月都有幾千蚊落袋 做零用錢<br />\n玩左幾個月，覺得真係好難做得好<br />\n落廣告又無一個準則，無人話比你聽做得正唔正確<br />\n有時落成千蚊 都無單返，有時又無啦啦 突然勁好生意<br />\n真係做到R哂頭<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/14/170547_766fa9df6ba3dc25d27e4a61cde86883.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2F170547_766fa9df6ba3dc25d27e4a61cde86883.png&h=f45e2832&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/14/170548_e87e69252bdfa609a8051a912e9edd1b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2F170548_e87e69252bdfa609a8051a912e9edd1b.png&h=af8afb47&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/14/170549_940d1630cbdba9b25328f81096f74aa9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2F170549_940d1630cbdba9b25328f81096f74aa9.png&h=5ede453e&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}